Soccer Goal-Line Technology Needs More Experimentation to Work, FIFA Says

-- B y   T a r i q   P a n j a
-- 
2011-03-05T13:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-05/soccer-rule-maker-says-goal-line-technology-needs-another-year-of-tests.html
Soccer’s rule-maker said 10 goal-
line technology systems it trialled weren’t satisfactory and
agreed to carry on experimenting for another year.  The International Football Asssociaton Board made the
decision at a meeting in Newport,  Wales  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tariq Panja at 
 tpanja@bloomberg.net  